      "text": "『誕生日にやりたいこと』、なんて書こうかな？\nなんでも叶えてくれるんだっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I write for \"Things I want to do on my birthday?\"\nIt's supposed to come true no matter what I write‚ right?",
