    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん……何、書いてるの？　あ、それ……\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan… what are you writing? Ah‚ that's…\nFrom \"Miracle☆Idol Birthday!\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7169377646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "事前アンケートだよ\nアイドル雑誌の有名企画、次は私の番なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a pre-interview questionnaire.\nIt's a famous project for an idol magazine‚ and it's my turn next!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう……！　このお仕事、楽しんでほしい……\nすみれちゃんの、やりたいことって……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations…! I hope you enjoy this project…\nSumire-chan‚ what do you want to do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7501575789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころが当ててみせましょう～\nずばり、トリエルのセンター強奪！　ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let Kokoro guess~.\nIt's gotta be stealing the center position in TRINITYAiLE‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ご、強奪！？　そんなことしないよー！\n無理矢理センターになっても嬉しくないし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Steal!? I wouldn't do that~!\nI wouldn't be happy becoming center by force!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2751242955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、私が書いたのは……\n『みんなとおしるこを作って食べたい』だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ what I wrote is…\n\"I want to make and eat oshiruko with everyone!\"",
